d at Shin Kai with a threatening grin. <br><br>Then Shin Kai looked upon the Temptress bound in the chair. This was Shin Kai's first look at the Rogue Temptress. He was young amongst the members of the Rose and had not yet made her acquaintance. <br><br>She was simply beautiful. Though beaten badly and bruised her attractiveness was evident. A single tear fell from her eye as she looked upon Takarae with hopelessness. She was all the more inviting. Beautiful, young and helpless. Shin Kai couldn't help but aid her as he could. After all she was a Rose and most beautiful at that. <br><br>Her lips were quivering and she shook from head to toe. Takarae gave her a smile to comfort her as he worked at the ropes that held her. As he did she screamed, his smile seemingly bringing her back to reality. &quot;NOOOOOOOOOO!&quot; <br><br>Her scream broke the dead air and like a trigger set off the fight (insert Matrix Sound Track)! Lord Galimont and his men jumped across the room as did Shin Kai and Veish'Kav! <br><br>(You Continue)<br><br> <p><HTML><CENTER><B><FONT SIZE="+1" COLOR="F8F8FF"><I>~ Shin-Kai Shinogi ~</I></FONT></B><BR><A HREF><CENTER><B><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF="http://www.eqrogue.com">ORDER of the BLACK ROSE</A></FONT></B></CENTER></A><a href><MARQUEE direction="left" loop="infinite" width="100%><font size="+1"><nobr><I>"Never sleep. Sleep is the cousin of Death...".</I></nobr></font></MARQUEE></a></HTML></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ushinkaiobr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shin Kai OBR</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0> at: 4/30/01 3:38:12 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#460000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uarctyc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arctyc</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Pos